Third-party components remain under their own licenses. Dual- or
multi-licensed crates show the SPDX license expression declared by the
upstream package on crates.io / in Cargo.toml. For dual-licensed crates
such as "Apache-2.0 OR MIT", recipients may use the software under either
license.

The Rust crate inventory below was generated from this repository with:

  cargo license --json

using the workspace members and Cargo.lock present at generation time.
