8. Regenerating this file
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

From the CPSL repository root:

  cargo install cargo-license
  cargo license --json > /tmp/cpsl-licenses.json
  # then update this document from the JSON inventory

Also re-check:

  - vendor/*/LICENSE*
  - optional PDFium binary licenses
  - cargo tree -i malachite
  - cargo tree -i cssparser

